    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines an abstract (generic, or base) YANG data model for network/service topologies and inventories.  The data model serves as a base model that is augmented with technology-specific details in other, more specific topology and inventory data models.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
